{"tid":367692,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"［孫子系列］龍狼傳而家係咪痴撚左線","createTime":"2017-08-21T02:48:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T03:36:12.000Z","uid":45017,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f9bc589201665477898d9424900dc634788047ee","tid":367692,"uid":45017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:48:14.000Z","msg":"屌你中學睇到而家都仲未完<br />\n我諗真係要等個孫燒比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一輯好好睇<br />\n中原繚亂篇已經開始on9<br />\n而家講志狼黎左咁撚耐先立志建國<br />\n近幾話仲要講埋羅馬<br />\n作者係咪痴撚左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049fa5e7d24ded3d6e4e3e4a976c3a339868b4a1","tid":367692,"uid":115525,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:50:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你中學睇到而家都仲未完<br />\n我諗真係要等個孫燒比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一輯好好睇<br />\n中原繚亂篇已經開始on9<br />\n而家講志狼黎左咁撚耐先立志建國<br />\n近幾話仲要講埋羅馬<br />\n作者係咪痴撚左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌佢老母<br />\n我又係中學睇到宜家<br />\n一開始睇佢努力訓練到成材就係為左條女係幾好睇<br />\n<br />\n但搵得返條女就好走啦<br />\n無啦啦執完一劑就擺條女係人地隔離 送比人地食<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9baafca0f2f56c0b596644be47fb128a3ab89537","tid":367692,"uid":70375,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:52:19.000Z","msg":"個陣時出埋pc game好正架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"093ebf8c59dd8e8eb30e10dc3ecf39cd02ff36ec","tid":367692,"uid":45017,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:54:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你中學睇到而家都仲未完<br />\n我諗真係要等個孫燒比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一輯好好睇<br />\n中原繚亂篇已經開始on9<br />\n而家講志狼黎左咁撚耐先立志建國<br />\n近幾話仲要講埋羅馬<br />\n作者係咪痴撚左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌佢老母<br />\n我又係中學睇到宜家<br />\n一開始睇佢努力訓練到成材就係為左條女係幾好睇<br />\n<br />\n但搵得返條女就好走啦<br />\n無啦啦執完一劑就擺條女係人地隔離 送比人地食<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n送比皇帝仔食<br />\n點知食撚完又要困完人<br />\n正宗中出即飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd62c0913d170d91dfb0a522dab72d45d45aadf","tid":367692,"uid":115525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:00:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌你中學睇到而家都仲未完<br />\n我諗真係要等個孫燒比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一輯好好睇<br />\n中原繚亂篇已經開始on9<br />\n而家講志狼黎左咁撚耐先立志建國<br />\n近幾話仲要講埋羅馬<br />\n作者係咪痴撚左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌佢老母<br />\n我又係中學睇到宜家<br />\n一開始睇佢努力訓練到成材就係為左條女係幾好睇<br />\n<br />\n但搵得返條女就好走啦<br />\n無啦啦執完一劑就擺條女係人地隔離 送比人地食<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n送比皇帝仔食<br />\n點知食撚完又要困完人<br />\n正宗中出即飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明明一開始睇佢修練爆撚哂氣真係好型棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f82a6b8fe4a1dd40e877329b22ad5748a270a4","tid":367692,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:05:05.000Z","msg":"唔係掉返轉等作者個孫繼續畫落去咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67094f28f4e8db11bd6f1ad76d5e039be2e8402b","tid":367692,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:05:50.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n<br />\n睇到匈奴已經覺得好唔對路<br />\n<br />\n個個角色變到蒼天之拳或北斗之拳畫風（連女角色都係走向肌肉畫風）<br />\n<br />\n而劇情同三國時代已經無乜關係"},{"pid":"ddb1596476139529b53b1bc2c981b5d98fc3103d","tid":367692,"uid":51453,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:06:43.000Z","msg":"打完仲達了?好耐無睇"},{"pid":"1b952a884340e4ffca981bc8510f4847b63df884","tid":367692,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:14:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打完仲達了?好耐無睇</blockquote><br />\n現在都唔知打乜鳩<br />\n<br />\n個個勢力都各懷鬼胎<br />\n<br />\n連龍之子都另起爐灶"},{"pid":"cb41444eec91d1defde79a7f31340a8c8765e469","tid":367692,"uid":39974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:19:40.000Z","msg":"每次睇都已經唔記得上集up乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33c50c70749ec5bcc9f6fefa27b8f680278746a","tid":367692,"uid":45017,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:20:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係掉返轉等作者個孫繼續畫落去咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都是孫子系列<br />\n不用分得那麼細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbcfe59540f9cc0b263f619b6eee711286e4849b","tid":367692,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:24:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每次睇都已經唔記得上集up乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最驚佢未畫完三國時代已經要腰斬<br />\n<br />\n佢開頭重講有日本既戰國時代"},{"pid":"295d54a7cb4330fb10e2ba2e1cde1314c9ed4623","tid":367692,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:33:46.000Z","msg":"仲有人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f38f5794c1fe85c89364c41a3dae575129b5d30","tid":367692,"uid":115525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:36:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打完仲達了?好耐無睇</blockquote><br />\n